<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5897] Nullcheck missing in CxfPayloadConverter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5897</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s a null-check missing in CxfPayloadConverter which triggers a NPE if the payload is the result from a SOAP Fault, in which case the CxfPayload object contains no body sources at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Stack trace, in this case what triggers type converters is Stream Caching, but it could happen in other cases where the FallbackConverter is utilized.&lt;/p&gt;

